            <title type='comp'>A Calendar Page of Mary Behrend: a digital transcription</title> <!-- ws-10-11-22: Titles are difficult, it seems like the titleStmt, seriesStmt, and sourceDesc would all say the same thing for this document. Should I not be including all of them? Should I be giving a title to the page that I transcribed? What about the 7 complied on newtfire?-->
            <author><persName>Behrend, Mary</persName></author>
            <respStmt><!-- ws-10-10-22: Please let me know if respStmt is correct, or if it should be ommited. Section 2.2.1 is behind reasoning for the inclusion. -->
