         <sourceDesc>
            <bibl>
               <title type="comp">A Calendar Page of Mary Behrend: a digital transcription</title> <!-- Refer to line 9 for this title. -->. In <author>Mary Behrend</author>, <title type='main'>1909 Calendar Pages</title>.
